:: Riding School Lesson
<<effects>>

<<if $riding_lesson is 0>>
	<<if $leftarm is "bound" or $rightarm is "bound">>
		"You can't ride like that," Remy says, untying your arms with deft movements. "Better."
		<<unbind>>
		<br><br>
	<</if>>
